      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) is a commercially validated code with documented V&V pedigree for cardiovascular applications. Version-controlled simulation scripts, documented change log, and regression test suite with 98% pass rate confirm Level 2 SQA compliance. All simulation files archived in institutional repository with SHA-256 checksums."
