      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/test-conditions-level2",
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented in FDA benchmark protocol. Blood analog fluid properties (viscosity, density) measured and reported with uncertainty bounds. Operating points (flow rate, rotational speed) match simulation boundary conditions within 1.5%. Temperature maintained at 37°C ± 0.5°C throughout testing. All five operating points span the clinical CPB envelope."
