      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/output-comparison-level2",
      "rationale": "Predicted hemolysis index compared against experimental measurements at all five operating points using the relative hemolysis index metric. Mean absolute error 8.3% is within the pre-specified 15% acceptance criterion. Pressure-flow curve agreement within 4.1% across the operating envelope. Systematic bias analysis shows no directional trend, confirming model adequacy."
