      "rationale": "Validation activities conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares geometric and operational characteristics with the device under assessment. Blood analog fluid used in validation experiments has documented rheological equivalence to human blood at CPB flow conditions. Operating conditions in validation span the full clinical CPB envelope. Validation-to-COU relevance gap analysis documented and judged acceptable."
