      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2 with a commercially validated solver, detailed numerical solver error quantification beyond code verification is scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance. The solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) has an established V&V pedigree for rotating machinery applications. Iterative convergence monitored to residual levels below 1e-6 for all equations in all simulations."
