      "rationale": "Use error assessment scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Simulation workflow is executed by credentialed CFD engineers with documented training records. Standard operating procedures govern mesh generation, boundary condition specification, and post-processing. Peer review of simulation setup completed by independent analyst prior to production runs."
