      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty assessment scoped out at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model are the established standard for FDA blood pump CFD submissions. Model form choices are consistent with FDA-recognized best practices and the validation evidence demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for the intended use."
